<i>noun</i>: 전광 [전ː광], 벼락 [벼락], 번갯불 [번개뿔/번갣뿔], 번개 [번개] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>전광 [전ː광]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightning</dd><br>
<dd>번개가 칠 때 번쩍이는 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>A light that flashes during a stroke of lightning.</dd><br>
<dd>2. being electric</dd><br>
<dd>전등의 불빛.</dd><br>
<dd>The light from an electric bulb.</dd><br>
<dt>벼락 [벼락]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightning</dd><br>
<dd>하늘에서 큰 소리를 내며 번쩍이는 빛의 줄기가 내리치는 자연 현상.</dd><br>
<dd>A natural phenomenon where a flash of light occurs in the sky accompanied by a loud boom.</dd><br>
<dd>2. harsh scolding</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 몹시 심한 야단이나 꾸지람.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An extremely severe reproof or scolding.</dd><br>
<dd>3. thunder; rush</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 매우 빠름.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The quality of being very quick.</dd><br>
<dd>4. sudden splash</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 예기치 않게 물을 뒤집어 씀.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) Having water poured on oneself unexpectedly.</dd><br>
<dt>번갯불 [번개뿔/번갣뿔]</dt><br>
<dd>lightning</dd><br>
<dd>번개가 칠 때 번쩍이는 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>The light that flashes during a thunderstorm.</dd><br>
<dt>번개 [번개]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightning</dd><br>
<dd>비가 내리는 중에 천둥소리와 함께 하늘에서 순간적으로 나는 번쩍이는 강한 빛.</dd><br>
<dd>A strong light flashing for a split second in the sky, along with the sound of thunder when it rains.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightning</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 동작이 아주 재빠르고 날랜 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A person who is very quick and deft in action.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>